{"tid":139111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣姨姨又有金句：法官係咪大晒？","createTime":"2017-03-01T06:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T11:47:36.000Z","uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"496e26b1735d6c5a7eb5a64a0b14cff7fc4a7b0a","tid":139111,"uid":41701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T06:58:33.000Z","msg":"七警襲擊罪成被判囚兩年，有支持警察的意見認為判刑過重，更有人建議設立量刑指引委員會，以民間組織監察法庭量刑，民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸亦表示支持。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員蔣麗芸的Facebook專頁昨分享了一段倡設量刑指引委員會的新聞，並表示：「法官係咪大哂（晒）？點算？法官判錯案，不受追究！市民有意見，不得干涉！」她認為成立民間組織監察法庭量刑，是可取的，亦支持陪審員制度伸延至地方法院。<br />\n<br />\n七警於月中被裁定「襲擊致造成身體傷害」罪成，蔣麗芸當時形容，七名警員是「不幸在被嚴重挑釁下」犯案，被判罪成令她心情沉重。<br />\n<br />\nlink: <a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E5%A4%A7%E6%99%92-%E8%94%A3%E9%BA%97%E8%8A%B8%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%A8%AD%E6%B0%91%E9%96%93%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E7%9B%A3%E5%AF%9F%E9%87%8F%E5%88%91/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2599%2592-%25E8%2594%25A3%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%258A%25B8%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E7%259B%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2588%2591%2F&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=cec5d383\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E7%2596%2591-%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25AE%2598%25E4%25BF%2582%25E5%2592%25AA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2599%2592-%25E8%2594%25A3%25E9%25BA%2597%25E8%258A%25B8%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E6%25B0%2591%25E9%2596%2593%25E7%25B5%2584%25E7%25B9%2594%25E7%259B%25A3%25E5%25AF%259F%25E9%2587%258F%25E5%2588%2591%2F&h=a05d8cb6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B3%AA%E7%96%91-%E6%B3%95%E5%AE%98%E4%BF%82%E5%92%AA%E5%A4%A7%E6%99%92-%E8%94%A3%E9%BA%97%E